<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday Sudeshna 🎂</title>
<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd6e8, #ffeaf4);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
    }.card {
    background: #fff0f6;
    border-radius: 25px;
    padding: 30px;
    width: 350px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.4);
}

h1 {
    color: #ff6fa5;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

p {
    color: #7a4b5c;
    font-size: 14px;
}

.cake {
    margin: 20px 0;
}

.candle {
    width: 10px;
    height: 30px;
    background: #ff85a2;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0 3px;
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 2px;
}

.flame {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: gold;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 0;
    animation: flicker 0.3s infinite;
}

@keyframes flicker {
    0% { transform: scale(1); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
    100% { transform: scale(1); }
}

button {
    background: #ff85a2;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    color: white;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

button:hover {
    background: #ff5c8a;
}

.game {
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.heart {
    font-size: 25px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

</style>
</head>
<body><div class="card">
    <h1>Happy Birthday Sudeshna 💖</h1>
    <p>You make life brighter, sweeter, and full of love ✨</p><div class="cake" id="cake">
    <div class="candle"><div class="flame"></div></div>
    <div class="candle"><div class="flame"></div></div>
    <div class="candle"><div class="flame"></div></div>
</div>.html